{"tid":1666561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政治衝擊 富臨賣舖 放售21億物業 優品棄租 3分店不續約","createTime":"2019-10-21T04:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T11:19:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f7d304c28592321e118cf705c63fdee783fc8a","tid":1666561,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20191020/A6O26YCRXR5I4OOJJN4NWOV3WI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191020%2FA6O26YCRXR5I4OOJJN4NWOV3WI%2F&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERWo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=db4e60c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191020%2FA6O26YCRXR5I4OOJJN4NWOV3WI%2F&h=419cfddd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20191020/A6O26YCRXR5I4OOJJN4NWOV3WI/</a><br />\n<br />\n政治衝擊<br />\n富臨賣舖 放售21億物業<br />\n優品棄租 3分店不續約<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】被指由「福建幫」打骰的富臨集團（1443）及優品360（2360），在近月的社會運動中成為眾矢之的，翻身成疑，最近兩品牌被迫變陣，前者開始放售旗下一籃子物業，後者棄租多個舖位。至於美心集團旗下元氣壽司，亦不續約兩舖「投降」。<br />\n<br />\n記者：王小羚<br />\n<br />\n據市場消息指，最近受政治衝擊較嚴重的富臨集團，見局勢不穩，開始縮減分店。由富臨或有關人士持有的 5個商舖及1項工廈物業，正低調放售，涉及放售金額達20.7億元。<br />\n<br />\n當中最貴重是荔枝角百老匯街114-118號美孚新邨第八期2樓至4樓129-133、135-137、145號舖，物業2樓為富園海鮮酒家，其餘樓層作出租用途，意向價4.9億元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/4kR4aLYYk8JInLl5g4t6Wn5OjSI=/732x485/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/NZDH73OMDIZB7FG5ZHFQ2FZA5E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F4kR4aLYYk8JInLl5g4t6Wn5OjSI%3D%2F732x485%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FNZDH73OMDIZB7FG5ZHFQ2FZA5E.jpg&h=8194e4bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨日九龍大遊行期間，示威者合力拉開優品360地舖的捲閘。何量鈞攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/6Mshbu1Binyp8rAJR8TA-R4F_M8=/732x485/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/BH5LXQHSZV3VSJAXIAZIT7TXRI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F6Mshbu1Binyp8rAJR8TA-R4F_M8%3D%2F732x485%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FBH5LXQHSZV3VSJAXIAZIT7TXRI.jpg&h=58fbe93e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n富臨集團在近期社會運動中成眾矢之的，屢受逆權市民狙擊。資料圖片<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n沙田兩舖共叫6億<br />\n<br />\n另由富臨或有關人士持有的兩項較貴重沙田物業，亦正放售。石門安群街1號京瑞廣場2期22樓201號舖，由富臨皇宮租回，每月租金約53.68萬元，現叫價4.5億元。沙田瀝源街7號沙田娛樂城4樓全層，面積達18,664方呎，連一個1,563方呎平台，現由富臨漁港及囍臨門自用，以交吉形式放盤，叫價1.5億元。<br />\n<br />\n至於同由富臨或有關人士持有、位於尖沙嘴金巴利道35-35A號金巴利中心地下A及B舖，及地庫A號舖，意向價4億元。該處現為炑八烤肉舖址，其他樓面則作出租。另同時放售一幢工廈，位於葵涌藍田街29號富臨中心全幢工廈，現有樓面面積約36,131方呎，以交吉形式交易，意向價2.9億元。<br />\n<br />\n一向被視為「福建御用飯堂」的富臨酒家，曾一度驚傳全線執笠，生意一落千丈。而富臨將旗下位於佐敦、馬鞍山和葵芳等酒樓，已改名「新苑」或「新馥」。據了解，這幾間分店早在逆權運動前，已售予新股東，撇清關係。而其他港九新界分店亦不排除轉售予新股東，同時因應局勢，除放售自用舖外，亦不乏減少租用分店數量。<br />\n<br />\n除富臨變陣外，多間零售舖遭到破壞的優品360，已棄租分店。市場更一度盛傳「舖王」鄧成波家族成員想頂手優品360，現該集團受零售寒冬影響，已減少租用物業，並棄租3個商舖，包括位於上環永樂街57至59號地下及閣樓，分別面積1,200及1,400方呎，租約至明年1月，業主現以每月23萬元放預租。另位於佐敦彌敦道318號地舖，面積800方呎，優品360在本月租期屆滿後不續約，原租金每月13萬元，業主減1萬元，以每月12萬元放租。<br />\n<br />\n此外，同是由優品360租用的香港仔湖南街8號地舖連閣樓，分別面積1,000及800方呎，在明年1月租期完結後不續租，該舖現正預租，租金每月18萬元。<br />\n<br />\n[img][<a href=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/auJ0OjAdVHCdVkL0GlxvBHK1oXI=/732x681/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/GFK2BG3RYMDDVF42NBTWN4M64E.gif[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FauJ0OjAdVHCdVkL0GlxvBHK1oXI%3D%2F732x681%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FGFK2BG3RYMDDVF42NBTWN4M64E.gif%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERWo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=c47cc674\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/auJ0OjAdVHCdVkL0GlxvBHK1oXI=/732x681/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/GFK2BG3RYMDDVF42NBTWN4M64E.gif[/img]</a><br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n元氣壽司棄租元朗兩舖<br />\n<br />\n據了解，優品360大股東林子峰亦積極放售持有的出租商舖，當中位於香港仔湖北街16號地舖及閣樓，面積分別920及800方呎，現以6,080萬元放售。<br />\n<br />\n該舖現由魚米以每月11萬元租用，租期至明年5月。本報查詢林子峰相關棄租事宜，他婉拒回應。<br />\n<br />\n至於同受政治衝擊影響的元氣壽司，亦棄租元朗兩舖，包括位於元朗西菁街10號好順泰大廈地下22及23號舖，面積1,423方呎，原本月租9.3萬元，租期至明年10月，現以10萬元放頂租。毗鄰的28及29號舖，亦原由元氣租下，面積2,100方呎，租期同樣至明年10月，原租金每月15萬元，現以每月14.6萬元放預租。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/_l4IlTuoog-0AEugGvEAALGj-po=/732x269/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/FIYCIZMM33HPK3WUD37IY7A2TE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F_l4IlTuoog-0AEugGvEAALGj-po%3D%2F732x269%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FFIYCIZMM33HPK3WUD37IY7A2TE.gif&h=557590c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAppleDaily"},{"pid":"3ad6bb072131377fab9dd58ef980710fa22167f2","tid":1666561,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:41:30.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05db5390075518bf827169aa8b6ce8e90dfab29","tid":1666561,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:49:57.000Z","msg":"初見成效<br />\n尚要努力"},{"pid":"c757c140c202e2c8bb7caaaaa3364d4c13dd0568","tid":1666561,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:50:36.000Z","msg":"點搞到佢賣唔出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d89c9d24d9b295f6268d1e6e07c58c56fae250d","tid":1666561,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:51:10.000Z","msg":"執柒左佢啦,呢班冚家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8148289478a09acb0e4d6351a2cebd19e943a954","tid":1666561,"uid":288231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:11:09.000Z","msg":"我想問如果藍業主既黃鋪點處理好"},{"pid":"861a487a68670f3fd41bae83e0ef0bae8a508b6a","tid":1666561,"uid":31324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8148289478a09acb0e4d6351a2cebd19e943a954","tid":1666561,"uid":288231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:11:09.000Z","msg":"我想問如果藍業主既黃鋪點處理好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:21:35.000Z","msg":"執幾億走都比佢賺到盡"},{"pid":"c70bf70c01f28ae0c7477635974c349844f5ddb5","tid":1666561,"uid":132056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:22:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天滅中共 全黨死清光</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d83ffa3b69bba01fac704dec88be5e122e6c647f","tid":1666561,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:24:02.000Z","msg":"邊個話冇用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21491045989812569cc0f2213a2db9b05ac4894","tid":1666561,"uid":289565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c757c140c202e2c8bb7caaaaa3364d4c13dd0568","tid":1666561,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:50:36.000Z","msg":"點搞到佢賣唔出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:03:15.000Z","msg":"開聲講 邊個敢買照搞 認住同地段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c250f460b8a342339091881c4e374eb425f9876d","tid":1666561,"uid":117893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2HDQesY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2HDQesY.png&h=bbc928bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢間鋪新開咗一個月，經過尋日九龍區遊行咁都無事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4592caedb754d81bf29bd3c9a1981f333b756e94","tid":1666561,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:19:00.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"}]}